- Click the â˜† on any card to star it, then toggle â˜… Starred in the chips.
- Click ğŸ”— Share to put the current search/filters/bundle/mode in the URL hash; copy the address.
- Use #ï¸âƒ£ Copy Numbered for a hearing/appeal/motion packet with numbering and headings.

